Subnetter [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/dckg/Subnetter.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/dckg/Subnetter)
====
Graphical program for solving  Robb Jones' "IPv4 Addressing and Subnetting Workbook", which is part of Cisco Networking Academy, CCNA1 course.

![Screenshot](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dckg/Subnetter/master/docs/img/Screenshot_20170316_135827.png)

# Requirements
## Running
* Proprietary Oracle JRE or OpenJFX. 
* Java 8 or higher
## Building
* JDK
---
## How to build 
Windows:
````
gradlew.bat build
````

Linux/UNIX
````
./gradlew build
````

----
This will generate a ``.zip`` under ``build/distributions`` directory, containing the application ``.jar`` and start scripts for each OS. 
## How to run
After building, zipfile contains under folder ``bin``
````
Subnetter-1.0
├── bin
│   ├── Subnetter
│   └── Subnetter.bat
└── lib
    └── Subnetter-1.0.jar
````
* a ``Subnetter.bat`` to start the application for Windows
* a shell script ``Subnetter`` for UNIX-like systems (Linux, Mac OS, ...)